<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;input
                type="checkbox"&gt; </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">允许你为表单中（或不在表单中）的提交项选择一个单一值。</span></span></li>
</ul>

                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">当</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">type</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">属性的值为</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">checkbox </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">时</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">这个属性的存在表示</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> input </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">是否默认被选中。你可以将该属性设置为</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">checked="checked"</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，或更简单地只设置为</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">checked</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">。</span></span></p>

                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">指定</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> input </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的值。如果省略，获取该元素的值的结果为字符串</span><span
